These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, documentary
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, surfing, ice-hockey
1. the person watching comedy movies is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
3. the person who's sport is skiing is the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | comedy | drama |
| Sport    | surfing    | ice-hockey | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
3 different pets are kept: hamster, cat, frog
City: venice, nizza, marseilles
1. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Pet       | cat | frog | hamster |
| City   | marseilles    | nizza     | venice        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
City: prague, berlin, hannover
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, pall-mall, oliveros
1. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| City         | hannover     | berlin | prague |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | bluemaster     | oliveros  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, water
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, balloon-flower, daffodil
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person drinking juice is the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Beverage   | water | almond-milk  | juice  |
| Flower         | lily  | balloon-flower | daffodil |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, hamster, mouse
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up, coffee
1. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Pet         | hedgehog   | mouse | hamster    |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee     | fanta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
3 different pets are kept: pony, horse, hedgehog
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, azure, apricot
1. the owner of the pony is the person who likes azure##1
2. the person who likes apricot is the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Pet   | horse | hedgehog | pony   |
| Color   | apricot     | black    | azure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, raspberry, carrot
House: cape-cod, townhouse, colonial
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the person eating lettuce is between the colonial house and the person eating carrot##2
3. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
4. the cape-cod house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Food   | carrot | lettuce | raspberry |
| House           | townhouse         | cape-cod         | colonial |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, rowing, snowboarding
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, fanta
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking mirinda and the person who's sport is climbing##2
2. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Sport   | rowing | snowboarding | climbing |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | hot-chocolate | fanta     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, havana, game
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, june, may
1. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Cigar   | game   | havana  | bluemaster  |
| Birthday         | may | june | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
