.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
House: palace, victorian, cottage
City: hannover, marseilles, new-york
1. the cottage house is on the right of the victorian house##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is the palace house##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is the cottage house##1
4. the cottage house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| House         | victorian | cottage | palace |
| City   | marseilles | new-york   | hannover |

