The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, october, may
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the wooden house is the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the palace house##3
4. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| House   | cape-cod | palace | wooden |
| Birthday     | october     | june   | may        |

