.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, d&b, reggae
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, time-travel, documentary
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is the fan of d&b##1
3. the fan of reggae is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | classical | d&b   |
| Movie-Genre         | time-travel | documentary   | thriller |

