.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, golf, weightlifting
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, pear
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is golf and the person eating kale##2
2. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating kale is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Sport   | golf | weightlifting | parkour |
| Food     | eggplant    | pear  | kale   |

