.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse, dog
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, tram
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Pet   | hedgehog  | dog     | mouse |
| Transport   | quad-bike | motorbike | tram    |

