.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-16::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, october, august
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, trike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person driving the trike is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Birthday          | august | june | october  |
| Transport   | quad-bike      | car  | trike |

