.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, alhambra, oliveros
House: futuristic, cottage, art-deco
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is in the middle##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is the cottage house##1
4. the futuristic house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Cigar         | oliveros | fonseca   | alhambra |
| House   | cottage   | futuristic | art-deco      |

