.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, dubstep, reggae
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, teacher, manager
1. the manager is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
2. the fan of house is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | house | dubstep | reggae |
| Job   | teacher   | manager          | librarian |

