.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, drawing
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, november, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Hobby     | puzzles  | drawing   | gardening |
| Birthday   | october | november | february       |

 